<p class="h1">FOLLOWERS OF THE WAY</p>
<p class="fl">Designation for Christians in the book of Acts (<a href="?bref=Acts.9.2">Acts 9:2</a>; <a href="?bref=Acts.19.9,23">19:9, 23</a>; <a href="?bref=Acts.22.4">22:4</a>; <a href="?bref=Acts.24.22">24:22</a>). In its early years, Christianity was called “the Way.” <span class="ital">See</span> <a href="?item=Waythe_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Way, The</a>.</p>
